That's where much
anxiety comes from.

00:20:35.030 --> 00:20:38.720 align:middle line:84%
People are taking too much
into consideration what

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:40.730 align:middle line:90%
others are thinking about them.

00:20:40.730 --> 00:20:43.160 align:middle line:84%
And interestingly enough,
others are more concerned

00:20:43.160 --> 00:20:44.800 align:middle line:84%
about what you're
thinking about them.

00:20:44.800 --> 00:20:46.802 align:middle line:84%
So everybody is living
in this false narrative

00:20:46.802 --> 00:20:49.260 align:middle line:84%
that people are thinking about
what they're thinking about.

00:20:49.260 --> 00:20:50.600 align:middle line:90%
And they're not.

00:20:50.600 --> 00:20:53.300 align:middle line:84%
And so one of the first
ways that you grow

00:20:53.300 --> 00:20:56.180 align:middle line:90%
is that you let the "they" go.

00:20:56.180 --> 00:20:58.820 align:middle line:84%
And you become aware that
there's something within you,

00:20:58.820 --> 00:21:04.410 align:middle line:84%
the great "I am," the singular
manifestation of a cosmic good

00:21:04.410 --> 00:21:05.630 align:middle line:90%
that's within you.

00:21:05.630 --> 00:21:08.300 align:middle line:90%
That becomes what you listen to.

00:21:08.300 --> 00:21:10.670 align:middle line:84%
And after a while, with
practice, meditation,

00:21:10.670 --> 00:21:14.060 align:middle line:84%
like visioning, et cetera, that
becomes the predominant voice

00:21:14.060 --> 00:21:15.500 align:middle line:90%
you hear.

00:21:15.500 --> 00:21:18.920 align:middle line:84%
You're living your
passion of the gift that

00:21:18.920 --> 00:21:20.870 align:middle line:90%
wants to come forward.

00:21:20.870 --> 00:21:22.610 align:middle line:90%
>> When times are tough--

00:21:22.610 --> 00:21:25.460 align:middle line:84%
you read stories of people who
went through the Holocaust,

00:21:25.460 --> 00:21:29.870 align:middle line:84%
or survivors from these
really horrific incidents.

00:21:29.870 --> 00:21:33.050 align:middle line:84%
And you think to yourself,
how did they do that?

00:21:33.050 --> 00:21:36.890 align:middle line:84%
They just did because humans
are-- we're inherently,

00:21:36.890 --> 00:21:39.200 align:middle line:90%
we're intrinsically resilient.

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:40.880 align:middle line:90%
But we never get tested.

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:42.740 align:middle line:84%
Think about how
safe our lives are.

00:21:42.740 --> 00:21:44.730 align:middle line:84%
We get up, we go to
work, we have a shower,

00:21:44.730 --> 00:21:46.022 align:middle line:90%
we have food when we come home.

00:21:46.022 --> 00:21:49.960 align:middle line:84%
We don't really get any of
these challenges in our lives.

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:52.220 align:middle line:84%
And so when something
really challenging

00:21:52.220 --> 00:21:54.770 align:middle line:84%
does happen to us,
or maybe something

00:21:54.770 --> 00:21:57.800 align:middle line:84%
that's not really that
challenging at all,

00:21:57.800 --> 00:22:00.470 align:middle line:84%
we fall apart because
we've had no practice.

00:22:00.470 --> 00:22:03.080 align:middle line:84%
We've never had to flex
our resilience muscle.

00:22:03.080 --> 00:22:05.810 align:middle line:84%
Having gone through all
of my life beforehand,

00:22:05.810 --> 00:22:08.810 align:middle line:84%
being a woman in a
male-dominated industry,

00:22:08.810 --> 00:22:10.940 align:middle line:84%
going to classes
at university where

00:22:10.940 --> 00:22:13.760 align:middle line:84%
you get told by your male
peers that you don't belong

00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:17.600 align:middle line:84%
in that class because you're
a woman, all of that stuff

00:22:17.600 --> 00:22:19.720 align:middle line:90%
made me more resilient.

00:22:19.720 --> 00:22:23.150 align:middle line:84%
And then my fire, my
fire experience, I guess,

00:22:23.150 --> 00:22:26.240 align:middle line:90%
just cemented that for me.

00:22:26.240 --> 00:22:28.610 align:middle line:84%
So what I did is I
would literally just

00:22:28.610 --> 00:22:31.590 align:middle line:90%
take each day as it came.

00:22:31.590 --> 00:22:35.180 align:middle line:84%
And every night before I went to
sleep, I'd think of the things

00:22:35.180 --> 00:22:36.650 align:middle line:84%
that I'd done really
well that day.

00:22:36.650 --> 00:22:38.240 align:middle line:84%
And I'd think of
the qualities that I

00:22:38.240 --> 00:22:42.450 align:middle line:84%
had that made me the perfect
prototype for this challenge.

00:22:42.450 --> 00:22:45.320 align:middle line:84%
>> I think it's really
important for everyone,

00:22:45.320 --> 00:22:47.420 align:middle line:84%
when they're going
through a difficult time,

00:22:47.420 --> 00:22:51.860 align:middle line:84%
to create their own declaration
and set their intention.

00:22:51.860 --> 00:22:53.960 align:middle line:84%
I don't know why
this is happening.

00:22:53.960 --> 00:22:56.120 align:middle line:84%
But one thing I know for
sure is something big,

00:22:56.120 --> 00:22:57.950 align:middle line:84%
something huge,
something way bigger

00:22:57.950 --> 00:23:00.080 align:middle line:84%
than me is going to
come out of this.

00:23:00.080 --> 00:23:04.650 align:middle line:84%
Because I'm not going through
all this stuff for nothing.

00:23:04.650 --> 00:23:08.940 align:middle line:84%
It's when you get stuck
in that negative space

00:23:08.940 --> 00:23:11.430 align:middle line:84%
that you don't see
the opportunities.

00:23:11.430 --> 00:23:13.170 align:middle line:90%
You're in this dark fog.

00:23:13.170 --> 00:23:14.515 align:middle line:90%
You're in that tunnel.

00:23:14.515 --> 00:23:17.310 align:middle line:84%
There could be a million
doors of opportunities

00:23:17.310 --> 00:23:18.110 align:middle line:90%
all around you.

00:23:18.110 --> 00:23:21.170 align:middle line:84%
You will never see them
because you're stuck.

00:23:21.170 --> 00:23:23.510 align:middle line:84%
When you are stuck,
it's like you

00:23:23.510 --> 00:23:25.670 align:middle line:90%
are staring at a closed door.

00:23:25.670 --> 00:23:28.700 align:middle line:84%
Not only is it closed,
but it's locked.

00:23:28.700 --> 00:23:31.730 align:middle line:84%
And what I mean by that is,
anytime you're complaining,

00:23:31.730 --> 00:23:34.370 align:middle line:84%
anytime you are feeling
sorry for yourself,

00:23:34.370 --> 00:23:36.403 align:middle line:84%
anytime you're saying,
why is this happening?

00:23:36.403 --> 00:23:37.820 align:middle line:84%
I can't believe
this is happening.

00:23:37.820 --> 00:23:39.470 align:middle line:90%
This isn't fair.

00:23:39.470 --> 00:23:43.650 align:middle line:84%
And all that resentment and
anger around your situation,

00:23:43.650 --> 00:23:48.020 align:middle line:84%
it's hard to move past that and
actually bounce back quickly.

00:23:48.020 --> 00:23:51.710 align:middle line:84%
>> What happens is, everything
is this energy based on thought

00:23:51.710 --> 00:23:53.472 align:middle line:90%
forms.

00:23:53.472 --> 00:23:55.430 align:middle line:84%
So you're afraid, you're
afraid, you're afraid.

00:23:55.430 --> 00:23:56.890 align:middle line:90%
You'd keep taking the steps.

00:23:56.890 --> 00:24:02.423 align:middle line:84%
And what happens is, fear gets
transmuted into excitement.

00:24:02.423 --> 00:24:03.590 align:middle line:90%
It's another form of energy.

00:24:03.590 --> 00:24:05.650 align:middle line:90%
It's a higher form of energy.

00:24:05.650 --> 00:24:08.300 align:middle line:84%
And when you keep
walking, excitement

00:24:08.300 --> 00:24:11.130 align:middle line:90%
gets transmuted into enthusiasm.

00:24:11.130 --> 00:24:13.460 align:middle line:84%
So you've gone from
fear to enthusiasm

00:24:13.460 --> 00:24:16.900 align:middle line:84%
by walking in the direction
of your dreams, you see.

00:24:16.900 --> 00:24:18.740 align:middle line:84%
So you don't let
it stagnate you.

00:24:18.740 --> 00:24:20.918 align:middle line:90%
Nor do you try to get rid of it.

00:24:20.918 --> 00:24:21.960 align:middle line:90%
You just acknowledged it.

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:23.060 align:middle line:90%
Oh, there's fear here.

00:24:23.060 --> 00:24:24.117 align:middle line:90%
Of course there's fear.

00:24:24.117 --> 00:24:25.700 align:middle line:84%
If you're doing
something you've never

00:24:25.700 --> 00:24:29.420 align:middle line:84%
done before, you're
stepping into the unknown,

00:24:29.420 --> 00:24:32.330 align:middle line:84%
then the egoic
structure, which does not

00:24:32.330 --> 00:24:36.350 align:middle line:84%
know the difference
between self-actualization,

00:24:36.350 --> 00:24:40.250 align:middle line:84%
or enlightenment, or
awakeness, transformation,

00:24:40.250 --> 00:24:43.675 align:middle line:84%
doesn't know the difference
between that and annihilation,

00:24:43.675 --> 00:24:46.740 align:middle line:84%
it projects fear
onto everything.

00:24:46.740 --> 00:24:48.660 align:middle line:90%
So you walk.

00:24:48.660 --> 00:24:49.665 align:middle line:90%
Fear becomes excited.

00:24:49.665 --> 00:24:51.540 align:middle line:90%
Oh, I'm excited.

00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:52.470 align:middle line:90%
And then I'm enthused.

00:24:52.470 --> 00:24:54.748 align:middle line:90%


00:24:54.748 --> 00:24:56.040 align:middle line:90%
You never know if you don't go.

00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:59.512 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:24:59.512 --> 00:25:22.380 align:middle line:90%


00:25:22.380 --> 00:25:26.010 align:middle line:84%
>> I've done stuff that I might
not never have put my hand up

00:25:26.010 --> 00:25:30.030 align:middle line:90%
for before my accident.

00:25:30.030 --> 00:25:32.670 align:middle line:84%
When I was running on the
Ironman course in Hawaii,

00:25:32.670 --> 00:25:36.720 align:middle line:84%
in Kona, just battling with
my internal demons, I'd go,

00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:39.390 align:middle line:84%
this is hard but it's
not as hard as what

00:25:39.390 --> 00:25:41.490 align:middle line:90%
you've been through before.

00:25:41.490 --> 00:25:45.240 align:middle line:84%
I guess my accident's given me
this really awesome reference

00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:49.190 align:middle line:84%
point for what is actually
a challenge in our world.

00:25:49.190 --> 00:25:52.580 align:middle line:84%
As now everywhere speaking in
front of thousands of people,

00:25:52.580 --> 00:25:53.710 align:middle line:90%
I'm like, yeah, it's hard.

00:25:53.710 --> 00:25:54.510 align:middle line:90%
I get scared.

00:25:54.510 --> 00:25:56.400 align:middle line:90%
I get anxious, for sure.

00:25:56.400 --> 00:26:00.930 align:middle line:84%
But it's not what I've
been through hard.

00:26:00.930 --> 00:26:03.630 align:middle line:84%
>> And as soon as we're done
going through this fire,

00:26:03.630 --> 00:26:04.510 align:middle line:90%
that's not the end.

00:26:04.510 --> 00:26:06.690 align:middle line:84%
It's not like we've
gone into the abyss,

00:26:06.690 --> 00:26:08.860 align:middle line:84%
we've discovered our
gifts, and end of story.

00:26:08.860 --> 00:26:09.660 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:26:09.660 --> 00:26:10.938 align:middle line:90%
Now is the return.

00:26:10.938 --> 00:26:13.230 align:middle line:84%
And this is the beautiful
part about the hero's journey

00:26:13.230 --> 00:26:15.670 align:middle line:84%
because we've gone
separation, initiation.

00:26:15.670 --> 00:26:17.920 align:middle line:90%
Now it's time for the return.

00:26:17.920 --> 00:26:19.920 align:middle line:84%
It's actually time to
take the gifts that you've

00:26:19.920 --> 00:26:23.017 align:middle line:84%
found about yourself,
about what your purpose is,

00:26:23.017 --> 00:26:24.600 align:middle line:84%
about what you're
here to do, and it's

00:26:24.600 --> 00:26:26.110 align:middle line:90%
time to bring them to the world.

00:26:26.110 --> 00:26:34.060 align:middle line:90%


00:26:34.060 --> 00:26:35.520 align:middle line:84%
So the return is
the exciting part

00:26:35.520 --> 00:26:37.170 align:middle line:84%
because we actually
get to take those gifts

00:26:37.170 --> 00:26:38.587 align:middle line:84%
and now share them
with the world.

00:26:38.587 --> 00:26:47.647 align:middle line:90%


00:26:47.647 --> 00:26:52.590 align:middle line:90%
[UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING]

00:26:52.590 --> 00:26:54.230 align:middle line:90%
>> Connection is within me.

00:26:54.230 --> 00:26:55.110 align:middle line:90%
It is me.

00:26:55.110 --> 00:26:58.120 align:middle line:84%
It's not like learning
rocket science.

00:26:58.120 --> 00:27:01.740 align:middle line:84%
It's not something I have
to gain from outside.

00:27:01.740 --> 00:27:03.720 align:middle line:90%
It is who I am.

00:27:03.720 --> 00:27:08.750 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about
going back to self.

00:27:08.750 --> 00:27:13.830 align:middle line:84%
And so meditation
is extraordinary.

00:27:13.830 --> 00:27:18.720 align:middle line:84%
Where we're going
is in the self.

00:27:18.720 --> 00:27:20.910 align:middle line:84%
And so the question, of
course, then becomes, well,

00:27:20.910 --> 00:27:22.050 align:middle line:90%
why can't I be like that now?

00:27:22.050 --> 00:27:23.250 align:middle line:90%
Why do I have to do anything?

00:27:23.250 --> 00:27:24.000 align:middle line:90%
Why meditate?

00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:24.540 align:middle line:90%
Why pray?

00:27:24.540 --> 00:27:25.340 align:middle line:90%
Why serve?

00:27:25.340 --> 00:27:29.700 align:middle line:84%
If it's me, why am I not able
to just live like that all

00:27:29.700 --> 00:27:31.320 align:middle line:90%
the time?

00:27:31.320 --> 00:27:35.820 align:middle line:84%
Because of all of that,
which is not self.

00:27:35.820 --> 00:27:38.865 align:middle line:84%
And this is where meditation is
such an extraordinary practice.

00:27:38.865 --> 00:27:41.490 align:middle line:90%


00:27:41.490 --> 00:27:46.560 align:middle line:84%
It helps us to let
go of the not self.

00:27:46.560 --> 00:27:50.700 align:middle line:84%
It's not that
meditation brings god,

00:27:50.700 --> 00:27:54.390 align:middle line:84%
or that meditation brings
peace and enlightenment.

00:27:54.390 --> 00:27:57.480 align:middle line:84%
Meditation removes that
which is keeping us

00:27:57.480 --> 00:28:00.600 align:middle line:84%
from seeing and living
in the divinity,

00:28:00.600 --> 00:28:03.390 align:middle line:84%
the light, the joy, the
peace that is who we are.

00:28:03.390 --> 00:28:06.690 align:middle line:90%


00:28:06.690 --> 00:28:13.170 align:middle line:84%
Whatever practice helps you
let go of the attachment--

00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:16.950 align:middle line:84%
I think for me personally,
I think when I'm meditating,

00:28:16.950 --> 00:28:20.040 align:middle line:90%
I think of a piece of Velcro.

00:28:20.040 --> 00:28:27.050 align:middle line:84%
And so the top layer is this
superficial level existence.

00:28:27.050 --> 00:28:30.660 align:middle line:84%
The role that I play, the
relationships that I have,

00:28:30.660 --> 00:28:33.090 align:middle line:84%
the physical body that
I have, all of that.

00:28:33.090 --> 00:28:34.700 align:middle line:90%
My history.

00:28:34.700 --> 00:28:40.740 align:middle line:84%
And the bottom part is the
truth of who I am, soul spirit.

00:28:40.740 --> 00:28:43.100 align:middle line:84%
And most of us live with the
two of them stuck together

00:28:43.100 --> 00:28:43.900 align:middle line:90%
all the time.

00:28:43.900 --> 00:28:48.030 align:middle line:84%
We have wrapped up our
awareness of soul self

00:28:48.030 --> 00:28:51.930 align:middle line:84%
with how much money you
make, who you're married to,

00:28:51.930 --> 00:28:53.950 align:middle line:84%
whose parent you are,
whose child you are,

00:28:53.950 --> 00:28:55.620 align:middle line:90%
how much you weigh.

00:28:55.620 --> 00:28:59.190 align:middle line:90%
And meditation is this.

00:28:59.190 --> 00:29:03.030 align:middle line:84%
It drops, and it
drops, and it drops.

00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:09.660 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, here I am sitting
in an awareness of soul spirit

00:29:09.660 --> 00:29:14.520 align:middle line:84%
that is dropped into that
ocean of the south that's

00:29:14.520 --> 00:29:20.100 align:middle line:84%
no longer stuck to the role,
the identity, the title,

00:29:20.100 --> 00:29:21.345 align:middle line:90%
the external object.

00:29:21.345 --> 00:29:24.040 align:middle line:90%


00:29:24.040 --> 00:29:27.580 align:middle line:84%
>> As a society, we're
constantly conditioned to chase

00:29:27.580 --> 00:29:30.740 align:middle line:90%
the next thing.

00:29:30.740 --> 00:29:32.870 align:middle line:84%
What it comes down
to, fundamentally,

00:29:32.870 --> 00:29:37.040 align:middle line:84%
is for the individual to
spend time with themselves.

00:29:37.040 --> 00:29:38.540 align:middle line:84%
And the beautiful
thing about this

00:29:38.540 --> 00:29:41.300 align:middle line:84%
is, it removes any
of the conditioning.

00:29:41.300 --> 00:29:43.880 align:middle line:84%
It removes any of the
board of directors

00:29:43.880 --> 00:29:45.200 align:middle line:90%
that maybe have been shut down.

00:29:45.200 --> 00:29:48.050 align:middle line:84%
It allows everyone to come to
the party and play the game.

00:29:48.050 --> 00:29:50.960 align:middle line:84%
Because when you're by yourself,
there's no one else telling you

00:29:50.960 --> 00:29:52.370 align:middle line:90%
what the answers need to be.

00:29:52.370 --> 00:29:55.980 align:middle line:90%


00:29:55.980 --> 00:29:58.170 align:middle line:84%
This is the beautiful
thing about life.

00:29:58.170 --> 00:30:01.012 align:middle line:84%
Not only are we destined
for something great.

00:30:01.012 --> 00:30:02.970 align:middle line:84%
Not only are we here to
do something incredible

00:30:02.970 --> 00:30:04.800 align:middle line:84%
with our lives, but we're
also given a blueprint

00:30:04.800 --> 00:30:05.730 align:middle line:90%
on how to do it.

00:30:05.730 --> 00:30:07.170 align:middle line:90%
That's the beautiful part.

00:30:07.170 --> 00:30:09.360 align:middle line:84%
So when you get quiet
enough, and you ask yourself,

00:30:09.360 --> 00:30:10.610 align:middle line:90%
what are you passionate about?

00:30:10.610 --> 00:30:13.110 align:middle line:84%
And really ask yourself,
and just sit with it.

00:30:13.110 --> 00:30:14.737 align:middle line:84%
This is it right
now in this moment.

00:30:14.737 --> 00:30:16.445 align:middle line:84%
And what kinds of
things are you good at?

00:30:16.445 --> 00:30:17.403 align:middle line:90%
And really sit with it.

00:30:17.403 --> 00:30:19.620 align:middle line:84%
And that's what this is
right now in this moment.

00:30:19.620 --> 00:30:20.940 align:middle line:90%
That's not anyone else.

00:30:20.940 --> 00:30:22.398 align:middle line:84%
That's not your
parents, that's not

00:30:22.398 --> 00:30:24.330 align:middle line:84%
society, that's not
anyone else telling you

00:30:24.330 --> 00:30:26.872 align:middle line:84%
what you need to do, or what
you need to be passionate about.

00:30:26.872 --> 00:30:29.130 align:middle line:84%
So you get to take
that as an individual

00:30:29.130 --> 00:30:30.720 align:middle line:84%
and follow that
as your blueprint.

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:32.490 align:middle line:84%
And when I say,
let's play pretend,

00:30:32.490 --> 00:30:33.990 align:middle line:84%
even if this sounds
crazy to you,

00:30:33.990 --> 00:30:35.070 align:middle line:84%
even if this sounds
so out there,

00:30:35.070 --> 00:30:36.300 align:middle line:90%
just try it on for a minute.

00:30:36.300 --> 00:30:38.100 align:middle line:84%
That the things that
you're passionate about,

00:30:38.100 --> 00:30:39.810 align:middle line:84%
the things that you're
good at, and the connection

00:30:39.810 --> 00:30:41.820 align:middle line:84%
you feel to the world,
the thing that you

00:30:41.820 --> 00:30:44.370 align:middle line:84%
want to change in
some way, or fix,

00:30:44.370 --> 00:30:47.700 align:middle line:84%
or have an impact with, pretend
like that isn't a coincidence

00:30:47.700 --> 00:30:50.310 align:middle line:84%
and that's an actual
blueprint for you to follow.

00:30:50.310 --> 00:30:51.613 align:middle line:90%
So it gives life meaning.

00:30:51.613 --> 00:30:52.530 align:middle line:90%
It gives life purpose.

00:30:52.530 --> 00:30:55.590 align:middle line:84%
